<!--<h4>First Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti sakavarṣa 938 neya rākṣasa saṁvatsara māgha
<lb n="2"/>suddha 5 Ādityavāradandu śrīmatu nūṟippadiṁba
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ra besadiṁ po(ṁ)ligoḷo<unclear>ḷu</unclear> poṁbaccada bālada <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="4"/>vṛtta <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>dhuradhoḷ</unclear> nūṟippadiṁbardvijaru besese goravā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ninājiyoḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> [Ari]mārbalamaṁ taḷtiṟidu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7"/><unclear>koṁda</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ryyavānaranā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> karṇna kāḷaga
<lb n="8" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> dirppa dhairyya
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nājiya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ge sarivo<unclear>ga</unclear>
</p>

<!--<h4>Fourth Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> radoḷu naḍedu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> bāḷtannevaraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> sivarāsijī
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> mmayya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> parōkṣa vineyadiṁ māḍi ka<unclear>lla</unclear>
<lb n="12"/>niṟisidōṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> jitēna labhyatē lakṣmīrmṛtēnāpi surāṁganā kṣaṇa vidhvaṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>si<unclear>ni</unclear> kāyē kā ciṁtā maraṇē raṇē
</p>

